DOC.brief_summary: To compare uroflowmetry measurements of patients undergoing urodynamic testing as part of an incontinence work-up in an urogynecology practice to healthy female volunteers.
DOC.brief_title: Uroflow Measurements in Urogynecology Patients Compared to Healthy Female Volunteers
DOC.criteria: All patients who underwent urodynamics at the urogynecology clinic during the past 12 months Voids larger than 50 mls. History of pelvic organ prolapse, incomplete bladder emptying, and voids less than 50cc.
